{"tid":1299974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地客撰吉澳鴨洲露營遊記　圖文教學捉海鮮煮大餐遭網民怒轟","createTime":"2019-07-09T08:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T16:39:36.000Z","uid":20689,"like":75,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"c62cfa5466f7e08c0c84d54c990b939c74d7d7a4","tid":1299974,"uid":20689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:23:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2395000/2395607/seafood_thumb_20190709_J_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2395000%2F2395607%2Fseafood_thumb_20190709_J_600.jpg&h=ff10107d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港有不少攝人的生態旅遊勝地，例如海岸公園、海岸保護區等，吸引遊客慕名而來，但都必須付上責任好好保護生態。近日有網民發現，有內地遊客撰寫吉澳、鴨洲遊記，疑非法露營及捕獲海鮮煮成大餐，遭網民怒轟！<br />\n<br />\n一名網民昨日（8日）在Facebook群組「香港行山遠足之友（吹水山谷）」發帖，表示有內地遊客在大陸網站「美篇」發文，撰寫一篇名為「香港吉澳離島沙灘露營」的遊記。該文章內容提及，一行10人於7月7日抵達吉澳及鴨洲，在無人海灣的沙灘上露營，並捕捉各種海洋生物煮成海鮮大餐。<br />\n<br />\n 內地遊客在海中捕獲海膽。（圖片來源：尋覓人生(何操) @ 美篇）<br />\n▲ 內地遊客在海中捕獲海膽。（圖片來源：尋覓人生(何操) @ 美篇）<br />\n<br />\n作者在遊記中提到，<br />\n<br />\n香港生態旅遊勝地，可遠眺深圳鹽田貨櫃碼頭，抓海膽、海螺、螃蟹、將軍鮑收穫滿滿，連續2天都是海鮮大餐。<br />\n從照片可見，他們捕獲了多箱海鮮，更自備煮食爐具即場烹煮海鮮。<br />\n<br />\n 他們捕捉了多種海洋生物，包括海膽、鮑魚、螃蟹，並自備爐具煮成海洋大餐。（圖片來源：尋覓人生(何操) @ 美篇）<br />\n▲ 他們捕捉了多種海洋生物，包括海膽、鮑魚、螃蟹，並自備爐具煮成海洋大餐。（圖片來源：尋覓人生(何操) @ 美篇）<br />\n<br />\n根據《郊野公園及特別地區規例》，除按照總監所批給的許可證的規定及在指定露營地點內，任何人不得在郊野公園或特別地區內露營或建立帳幕或臨時遮蔽處。<br />\n<br />\n據漁護署資料顯示，香港郊野公園現設41個露營地點，吉澳和鴨洲不屬在內，因此在該處露營有可能觸犯法例。<br />\n<br />\n網民得悉事件後，一律留言炮轟內地客自私的行為，<br />\n<br />\n生態大災難！<br />\n海裡的生物遲早被你們吃光！<br />\n咁細隻都唔放過，直情未發育完成！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2395607/%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%AE%A2%E6%92%B0%E5%90%89%E6%BE%B3%E9%B4%A8%E6%B4%B2%E9%9C%B2%E7%87%9F%E9%81%8A%E8%A8%98%E3%80%80%E5%9C%96%E6%96%87%E6%95%99%E5%AD%B8%E6%8D%89%E6%B5%B7%E9%AE%AE%E7%85%AE%E5%A4%A7%E9%A4%90%E9%81%AD%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E6%80%92%E8%BD%9F?r=cpsdfb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2395607%2F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%2592%25B0%25E5%2590%2589%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%25B4%25A8%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E9%259C%25B2%25E7%2587%259F%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A8%2598%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%259C%2596%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%258D%2589%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%25AE%25AE%25E7%2585%25AE%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%25A4%2590%25E9%2581%25AD%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2580%2592%25E8%25BD%259F%3Fr%3Dcpsdfb&d=R%2BBR62t8sBL7FL0rmd5Y1UzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=33d8ec52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2395607/%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%AE%A2%E6%92%B0%E5%90%89%E6%BE%B3%E9%B4%A8%E6%B4%B2%E9%9C%B2%E7%87%9F%E9%81%8A%E8%A8%98%E3%80%80%E5%9C%96%E6%96%87%E6%95%99%E5%AD%B8%E6%8D%89%E6%B5%B7%E9%AE%AE%E7%85%AE%E5%A4%A7%E9%A4%90%E9%81%AD%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E6%80%92%E8%BD%9F?r=cpsdfb</a>"},{"pid":"4dd37d777d75cf3a1d3542d15cd394a8ea459aa9","tid":1299974,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f55ca22514842563e6ba608514f8b3b4abdaa30","tid":1299974,"uid":14494,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:26:34.000Z","msg":"喇 呢d就要send上藍絲谷喇"},{"pid":"051188a91bf4e310d05385ece2d9968ff6f23369","tid":1299974,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:31:08.000Z","msg":"有無方法放D加料既海鮮落去比班仆街捉？"},{"pid":"775bf90ee57ea97b6938f72d0fd55d1decfe2010","tid":1299974,"uid":81505,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"9f55ca22514842563e6ba608514f8b3b4abdaa30","tid":1299974,"uid":14494,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:26:34.000Z","msg":"喇 呢d就要send上藍絲谷喇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:38:39.000Z","msg":"藍絲同佢地差唔多<br />\n試過去去露營<br />\n格離有5，6個廢中<br />\n用晒最靚既營<br />\n傍晚就藍牙喇叭大聲播歌<br />\n支直立營燈2點幾開到最光<br />\n透到我個營，好刺眼<br />\n又大聲傾計<br />\n要我出去指住佢個頭屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e03f8c31e7d3332ffa5466a2bed4a3eeecf3e027","tid":1299974,"uid":20689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:59:52.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"a59092989b2be872f8f5aff0f5ca06b3e505c5b2","tid":1299974,"uid":81113,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:00:23.000Z","msg":"而家政府咩都唔做<br />\n小巿民就日日夜夜都要光復"},{"pid":"e01248bf0f37fc16ca73873a6d4ce44ccde08a4f","tid":1299974,"uid":26942,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:02:12.000Z","msg":"呢d 就要去光復啦"},{"pid":"f29739f1bcae22af5f1f8a7b43e2e920ae2fc2c6","tid":1299974,"uid":70336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:06:46.000Z","msg":"召喚777<br />\n<br />\n仆街 召喚失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e88ecc3a783f5df60d93aa1dcf4e81014967a78a","tid":1299974,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62bac9ac9b1d3c9792f54a090ca6b60954e94ac","tid":1299974,"uid":161185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:00:22.000Z","msg":"不知所謂"},{"pid":"6ed5130e7c0545c9833dd6ddcf1cdf502dce254c","tid":1299974,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:02:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70d9e992ec365add6f1fdc19099464428bb9264a","tid":1299974,"uid":78913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c460f35